- hfsplus module :
  run command 'modinfo hfsplus' to check if you have hfsplus module

- dmg2img :
  site		: http://vu1tur.eu.org/tools/
  download	: http://vu1tur.eu.org/tools/dmg2img-1.6.5.tar.gz

- udisks2 :
  site		: http://www.freedesktop.org/wiki/Software/udisks/
  download	: http://udisks.freedesktop.org/releases/

- You need to be in the 'disk' group.

- Darling (optional : required to use --run)
  site		: http://www.darlinghq.org
  git		: https://github.com/LubosD/darling
  instructions	: http://www.darlinghq.org/build-instructions
